WEBVTT

00:01.211 --> 00:04.576
You kill people, don't you?

00:04.601 --> 00:06.890
<i>I go to this border town
for a little R&R.</i>

00:06.953 --> 00:08.061
Kill or be killed.

00:08.117 --> 00:09.427
And I've been using
your place as a safe house.

00:09.451 --> 00:11.218
I hope that's okay.

00:11.253 --> 00:12.463
I thought perhaps
your partner going to prison

00:12.487 --> 00:13.553
<i>may have given you pause.</i>

00:13.588 --> 00:15.488
People kept needing me.

00:15.524 --> 00:16.801
<i>We don't murder perfectly
healthy individuals</i>

00:16.825 --> 00:18.257
<i>who happen to be a bit sad.</i>

00:18.293 --> 00:20.293
Buddy, no!

00:20.328 --> 00:22.829
<i>Well, in Switzerland,
a doctor would give a patient</i>

00:22.864 --> 00:27.500
<i>such as yourself a lethal dose
of sodium pentobarbital,</i>

00:27.536 --> 00:29.435
<i>to drink.</i>

00:29.470 --> 00:31.081
Jess, I have some of your dad's
things that he left here.

00:31.105 --> 00:32.283
Would you see that
he gets them, please?

00:32.307 --> 00:33.839
Sure.

00:33.874 --> 00:34.840
And I don't think we should
only help people

00:34.875 --> 00:36.575
when it's easy for us.

00:36.610 --> 00:38.277
We also have to be able
to sleep at night.

00:38.313 --> 00:40.146
<i>The first death
I do with you ends</i>

00:40.181 --> 00:42.781
<i>with a woman flinging
herself off a balcony,</i>

00:42.817 --> 00:45.016
<i>and then you welcome
Grady's sister into our lives.</i>

00:45.052 --> 00:46.585
<i>I didn't.
She took advantage of me.</i>

00:46.620 --> 00:48.286
I'm gonna need you
to kill my husband.

00:48.322 --> 00:50.355
Mary she said it was... it was
either him or me.

00:50.390 --> 00:52.023
I'm the woman who
killed your brother.

00:52.059 --> 00:53.492
A cop killed my brother.

00:53.527 --> 00:54.993
A cop may have pulled
the trigger,

00:55.028 --> 00:57.663
but I let Grady
bleed out and die.

00:57.698 --> 01:02.000
If you ever mess with me or Des
again, I will kill you too.

01:02.035 --> 01:03.468
Just a bad couple of days.

01:03.503 --> 01:04.780
It's growing pains or something.

01:04.804 --> 01:06.304
I just want to help people,

01:06.340 --> 01:10.108
Des, and when
I do it alone, I can.

01:10.143 --> 01:12.543
You'll feel a rush
through your body,

01:12.579 --> 01:14.812
and then a warm feeling
of peacefulness

01:14.848 --> 01:17.349
will take you slowly into sleep.

01:17.384 --> 01:20.217
You can press it again and
again.

01:22.000 --> 01:28.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

02:55.079 --> 02:57.244
What does it mean?

02:57.280 --> 03:02.450
Don't be afraid.
Love does not kill.

03:02.485 --> 03:07.789
It's life itself, and it shines
with heavenly joys.

03:07.824 --> 03:08.957
That's beautiful.

03:11.127 --> 03:12.594
It's my first time.

03:12.629 --> 03:15.096
I had no idea
it was so powerful.

03:15.131 --> 03:17.465
We haven't even gotten
to the good stuff.

03:27.443 --> 03:29.943
To the finale.

05:24.473 --> 05:27.636
<font color="#33FF00">Mary Kills People 02x02</font> <font color="#3399FF">The Connection</font>
